{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"k0qo53e6jvew0mcyv49bu0e","title":"Publish","desc":"","updated":1661970817297,"created":1661540036400,"custom":{},"fname":"publish","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"},"contentHash":"200c046fbcf21757c0e1964e58443998","links":[],"anchors":{"to-compile-document":{"type":"header","text":"To Compile Document","value":"to-compile-document","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"export-markdown-pod":{"type":"header","text":"Export Markdown Pod","value":"export-markdown-pod","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"pandoc":{"type":"header","text":"Pandoc","value":"pandoc","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"resources":{"type":"header","text":"Resources","value":"resources","line":31,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["p6evbyfciaotkrkwav3ipra","mg7066wnd3agqrjxcxmrxkx"],"parent":"nuyfwd7iokzd7m9oax0cdx5","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"publish\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#publish\"></a>Publish</h1>\n<h2 id=\"to-compile-document\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#to-compile-document\"></a>To Compile Document</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Run <code>compile_paper.sh</code>\n<ul>\n<li>This currently is slightly broken  due to <code>./</code> prepend path issue with pandoc<a href=\"https://github.com/dendronhq/dendron/issues/3460\">Pod V2 export asset paths</a></li>\n<li><strong>Key</strong> as long as all paths of note assets have <code>./</code> prepended the output should be proper.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"export-markdown-pod\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#export-markdown-pod\"></a>Export Markdown Pod</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Configure markdown pod through command palette</li>\n<li>Export pod to folder pod_export</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"pandoc\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pandoc\"></a>Pandoc</h2>\n<p>From root directory run:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-{bash}\"><code class=\"language-{bash}\">pandoc -f gfm --toc -s pod_export/Parameter_Estimation/Paper.md -o paper.docx --reference-doc=reference.docx\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><code>-f</code> format GitHub ... something style\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> Look up later</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>--toc</code> - table of contents</li>\n<li><code>-s</code> - standalone</li>\n<li><code>-o</code> - output</li>\n<li><code>--reference-doc</code> - reference for word formatting. Change this docs formatting to change the export formatting.</li>\n<li><strong>Note</strong>: Can also use this to export to word</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"resources\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#resources\"></a>Resources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/Un0n1ql7LfvMtmA9JEi4n/\">config.export info</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/Parameter_Estimation/notes/p6evbyfciaotkrkwav3ipra\">Pdf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Parameter_Estimation/notes/mg7066wnd3agqrjxcxmrxkx\">Word</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"nuyfwd7iokzd7m9oax0cdx5","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1662428184246,"created":1661538521294,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"},"contentHash":"9185b031f95deeced1275adbefc49c09","links":[],"anchors":{"parameter_estimation":{"type":"header","text":"Parameter_Estimation","value":"parameter_estimation","line":7,"column":0,"depth":2},"paper-export":{"type":"header","text":"Paper Export","value":"paper-export","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["m7o7r4jqe4jdwgsh3ia8sa4","2fib55e8qqux9scimc7a9gn","tz8wfy0bidyoi7cew6pxfi4","k0qo53e6jvew0mcyv49bu0e","xxezmgby3v2mlneka3t295g","9gt33emg7725ksj2t7f4p4v"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"## Parameter_Estimation\n\n## Paper Export\n- [paper.docx](./notes/export/paper.docx)\n- [paper.pdf](./notes/export/paper.pdf)"},"collectionChildren":